This paper is about improving the search quality in personal email search using a novel neural model. The paper discusses the use of deep learning-to-rank models and proposes a new model called SepAttn. The paper involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques such as n-gram embeddings and attention mechanisms, which are commonly used in the sub-categories of information retrieval (cs.IR), computational linguistics (cs.CL), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL). Therefore, these sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
